  "description": "In Japan, the country that inspired the slogan \"Born to be Mild,\" the blood of young men still runs hot. In the old days they'd go off into the country and hack each other up with swords, but these days, what with school, that isn't very practical. <br><br>\nSo some of them do something very un-Japanese. They strap on a big bike, roar around annoying people, and pound anyone they consider dishonorable. <br><br>\nNow meet Eguchi Yousuke, leader of a high-school Biker gang AND the school's handicrafts club. Which means he divides his time between fistfights and fancy needlework. <br><br>\nAnd if you think he's weird, wait until you meet the rest of his gang... <br><br>\n(Source: AniDB)",
